Class Project

Object
Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a BTO housing project managed by HDB. A project contains information about available flats, application periods, and is managed by an HDB Manager.
Since:
2025-03-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
SC2002 G Team

    • Project

      public Project(String projectId, String projectName, String neighborhood, Map<FlatType,Integer> flatTypes, Date applicationOpeningDate, Date applicationClosingDate, HDBManager managerInCharge, int availableOfficerSlots)
      Creates a new Project with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      projectId - The unique identifier for this project
      projectName - The name of this project
      neighborhood - The neighborhood where this project is located
      flatTypes - Map of flat types and their quantities
      applicationOpeningDate - The date when applications open
      applicationClosingDate - The date when applications close
      managerInCharge - The HDB Manager in charge of this project
      availableOfficerSlots - Number of HDB Officers that can handle this project
